This repo contains a MapReduce implementation of Vector Space Model of Information Retrieval. 

Scripts : 
1. MapReduce.py - implements mapreduce in python
2. vs_inverted_index - computes inverted index of tf-idf vectors
3. length.py - computes lengths of tf-idf vectors
4. alpha.py - computes cosine similarity with a specific query and returns documents ordered to their relevance. 

Procedure : 
Offline - 
1. python vs_inverted_index "input_corpus_of_documents" > index
2. python length index > vector_lengths
Online - 
1. Enter the query in alpha.py
2. python alpha.py vector_length index > output
